  "description": "Todas las cartas — a browsable gallery of the full 22-arcana deck, reached from a new slide-in app menu. The gallery renders every card face-up in a three-column grid and tapping one deep-links to its reading; it draws and stores nothing. The menu, opened by the header star, slides in over any screen from shared context. This session refactored NavMenu into MenuBackdrop, MenuHeader and MenuItem sub-components, reduced the gallery page to pure composition, and extracted a tested menuPanelWidth helper.",
